<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١١٧:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{وَاذْكُرْنَ مَا يُتْلَى فِي بُيُوتِكُنَّ مِنْ آيَاتِ اللَّهِ وَالحِكْمَةِ}</span> <span class="c4">[الأحزاب: ٣٤]</span>:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> آيَاتِ اللَّهِ: القُرْآنِ ,<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَالحِكْمَةُ:</span> السُّنَّةُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>